 -- Sergei Golovan <sgolovan@debian.org>  Fri, 01 Oct 2021 13:54:07 +0300

erlang (1:24.1+dfsg-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Refresh patches.
  * Replace calls to 'which', which is deprecated, by calls to
    'command -v' in maintainer scripts.
  * Mark the erlang, erlang-doc, erlang-examples, erlang-nox, erlang-src,
    erlang-x11 packages as multi-arch foreign.
  * Move epmd.service and epmd.socket to /usr/lib/systemd/system/.
  * Bump standards version to 4.6.0.

 -- Sergei Golovan <sgolovan@debian.org>  Tue, 28 Sep 2021 10:15:57 +0300

