erlang (1:24.0~rc2+dfsg-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release candidate.
  * Refresh patches.
  * Rename another PATH_MAX occurrence to enable build for GNU/Hurd and
    GNU/kFreeBSD.
  * Adapt debian/watch to the currently implemented release scheme.

 -- Sergei Golovan <sgolovan@debian.org>  Fri, 26 Mar 2021 15:44:51 +0300

erlang (1:24.0~rc1+dfsg-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release candidate.
  * Refresh patches.
  * Remove obsolete patch which adapted erlang-wx to wxwidgets-3.0.
  * Remove obsolete patch which fixed a function prototype in beam_load.c.
  * Remove the erlang-base-hipe binary package because HiPE support has been
    dropped upstream in favor of JIT.
  * Add libwxgtk-webview3.0-gtk3-dev to the list of build dependencies to
    enable webview support in erlang-wx.

